NAME

    Monitis Perl - API Perl interface for Monitis, all-in-one IT monitoring platform (http://www.monitis.com)


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

EXAMPLES

    See 'eg' directory of this distribution for examples.

DEPENDENCIES

    LWP::UserAgent
    JSON
    Digest::SHA
    HTTP::Message
    Test::Simple


